{"word":"κάτοπτος","slug":"κάτοπτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κάτοπτος</b></el> <el>(κάτοπτος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ὄψομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> of <a href='S:ὁράω'><el>ὁράω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be seen, visible</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>in view of</i> or <i>looking down over</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}